Hi all! 

 I completed&nbsp;my MA in English Language Teaching (ELT) at Jahangirnagar University, Savar, Dhaka, and this dissertation partially fulfilled my MA degree in ELT. This was my first work, and I edited some errors before publishing it online. I hope it&nbsp;will help a bit in researching EFL Classroom Management. If anyone gets help a bit, I will be happy and enthusiastic.&nbsp; 

 Researcher

